                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When a magnegor takes damage from a metal weapon or an effect with the metal trait, it takes @Damage[5[untyped]] additional damage and must succeed at a @Check[type:flat|dc:5] or become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1}. The value of the sickened condition increases each time the magnegor fails such a check, to a maximum of 3.</p>"
